title: Finding Yourself & Getting Out Of Your Comfort Zone with Aaron Idelson
itunes:title: Finding Yourself & Getting Out Of Your Comfort Zone with Aaron Idelson
description:
Brooke goes solo and talks to her longtime friend and fellow podcaster, Aaron Idelson!  The duo discuss all things college, “adulting”, embracing and loving who you are & more!

Check out MJ Custom Tie Dye: https://instagram.com/mjcustomtiedye?igshid=1tw1y5w1v2mut 

Thank you to Aaron for coming on the show!  Check out Aaron’s socials and show him some love:
@aaronidelson @queeringtheairpod
